ContentDesc_Arkadion - Superschwergewich: Having heard your direct account of your rise through the heavyweight division, Gabbro's imagination runs wild once more. Indeed, he now envisions a world where Vamp Fatale's spectacle of slaughter were a further nightmarish affair. Had her punishment been even more severe, would she have brought you to your knees?
Instancecontenttextdata_40708_Text: What power! Looks like someone isn't holding back!
Instancecontenttextdata_40709_Text: Such potent magicks! But will they be enough to turn the tide?
Instancecontenttextdata_40711_Text: Oh dear! The challenger has fallen out of the ring!
Instancecontenttextdata_40725_Text: Oof, that must've hurt! Hang in there!
Instancecontenttextdata_40730_Text: And they dance out of the way unharmed! Unbelievable!
Instancecontenttextdata_40733_Text: Oh no, they've been felled with a vengeance!
Instancecontenttextdata_40734_Text: And they're down! Can they recover from this?
Instancecontenttextdata_40736_Text: And they're back in action! Can they turn the tide!?
Instancecontenttextdata_41925_Text: You cannot escape from the wolf!
Instancecontenttextdata_43501_Text: Hahaha... Will you cry out in pleasure, or pain?
Instancecontenttextdata_43502_Text: Feast your eyes on the lovely─and lethal─Vamp Fatale!
Instancecontenttextdata_43503_Text: Will the challenger fall prey to the cruel mistress?
Instancecontenttextdata_43505_Text: This is my show. I will hear you scream.
Instancecontenttextdata_43506_Text: A wicked weapon! Vamp Fatale's poised to execute a fatality!
Instancecontenttextdata_43507_Text: You will become a stain on this ring.
Instancecontenttextdata_43508_Text: The challenger has nowhere left to run!
Instancecontenttextdata_43510_Text: It's begun! She's draining the audience─of their aether!
Instancecontenttextdata_43511_Text: All of you will feed me.
Instancecontenttextdata_43512_Text: Vamp Fatale's unleashed the aether! The challenger's in her realm now!
Instancecontenttextdata_43514_Text: The spectacle of slaughter resumes! How will the challenger adapt?
Instancecontenttextdata_43515_Text: It's a veritable rain of death!
Instancecontenttextdata_43516_Text: Such insolence I have never known! More─I need more aether!
Instancecontenttextdata_43517_Text: She's draining the crowd's aether again! I hope our dear spectators are feeling alright...
Instancecontenttextdata_43519_Text: She's unleashed even more aether! How will this end!?
Instancecontenttextdata_43521_Text: It's still not enough. I will take everything you have!
